snippet: Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang scored twice in the first 18 minutes as Borussia Dortmund trounced Galatasaray 4-0 to maintain their status as Group D leaders in the Champions League on Wednesday....

headline.print_headline: Dortmund Crush Galatasaray to Maintain 100 Percent Record
headline.main: Dortmund Crush Galatasaray to Maintain 100 Percent Record

lead_paragraph: Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang scored twice in the first 18 minutes as Borussia Dortmund trounced Galatasaray 4-0 to maintain their status as Group D leaders in the Champions League on Wednesday.
